### Environment variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080

################################
### Test Endpoints ###
################################

### Check if backend is running
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test/public

### Test CORS functionality
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test/cors-test
Origin: http://localhost:5173

### Test authentication endpoint
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/test

### Register new user
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/signup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!",
  "role": "STUDENT"
}

### Login
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "Password123!"
}

### Store token from login response
@token = {{login.response.body.accessToken}}

### Try protected endpoint with token
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/test/protected
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Submit parent request
POST {{baseUrl}}/parent/requests
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "parentName": "Test Parent",
  "childName": "Test Child",
  "childAge": "10",
  "requestDetails": "Need help with mathematics"
}

### Submit teacher application
POST {{baseUrl}}/teacher/apply
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teacherName": "Test Teacher",
  "qualifications": "Masters in Education",
  "experienceYears": "5",
  "subjects": "Mathematics, Science"
}

### Submit school request
POST {{baseUrl}}/school/request
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "schoolName": "Test School",
  "contactPerson": "School Admin",
  "contactEmail": "school@example.com",
  "requestDetails": "Need math and science teachers"
}

### Test dashboard access
GET {{baseUrl}}/dashboard
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

### Test CORS (browser will check preflight)
OPTIONS {{baseUrl}}/api/test/public
Origin: http://localhost:5173
Access-Control-Request-Method: GET
Access-Control-Request-Headers: Content-Type
